          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The (g,n) and  (g,p)  cross  section  in  160Gd  were",
                " measured from    threshold    to    33   MeV   using",
                " bremsstrahlung from 33 MeV betatron and observing the",
                " induced activities.  Both  cross  sections contain a",
                " broad maximum at 23.5 MeV.  It is argued  that  this",
                " maximum is the quadrupole resonance predicted at 1.6",
                " times the  E1  giant   resonance   energy   by   the",
                " hydrodinamic model."
              ]
            }
          ],
